# Forms Guide

- Use shadcn/ui components for all form fields (e.g., `Input`, `Label`, `Button`).
- Layout forms in a single column with tight vertical spacing (`space-y-4`).
- Place forms inside a card-like container with `bg-white`, `border border-gray-200`, and `rounded-lg`.
- Use clear, concise labels for each field.
- Validate fields using zod schemas and show errors directly below the relevant field in small red text.
- Use toast notifications for form-level feedback (e.g., authentication failure) via the `sonner` package. See [login.tsx](mdc:src/routes/auth/login.tsx) for usage.
